WORLDWIDE RESORTS INTERACTIVE DASHBOARD (DASH APP)

This project is an interactive resort recommendation dashboard built with Plotly Dash in Python.
It allows users to explore global ski resorts across all continents and filter them based on preferences such as price, skiing conditions, and amenities.

The app helps users quickly identify the best resort options based on budget, region, and ranking metrics.

KEY FEATURES
ðŸ”¹ Tab 1 â€” Map of Skiing Hotspots
A global scatter_mapbox visualization plotting all ski resorts.
Interactive filters allow users to tailor results based on:
-Maximum Price Slider
-Summer Skiing (checkbox)
-Night Skiing (checkbox)
-Resorts with Snowparks (checkbox)
The filters update the map live, helping users visually locate suitable destinations.

ðŸ”¹ Tab 2 â€” Country & Resort Report
A multi-column analytical layout:
1. Sidebar Filters
-Select a Continent
-Automatically update a second dropdown to show Countries in the selected continent
-Select a performance metric to visualize (e.g., price, elevation, slopes, cannons, etc.)
2. Top 10 Resorts Bar Chart
-Bar chart showing the top 10 resorts in the chosen country
-X-axis shows resort names (labels optionally removed for readability)
-Y-axis shows the user-selected metric

Helps with ranking & quick comparison

3. Resort Report Card
Displays key information about the selected resort, including:
-Resort Name
-Elevation Rank
-Slope Rank
-Price Rank
-Cannon Rank

TOOLS & TECHNIQUES
Python, Pandas, Plotly Express, Dash, Html, CSS, Dash Bootstrap Components, Dash Bootstrap Templates
                            
